*.key
credentials.json
secrets.json

# Merge / editor noise
*.orig
*.rej
*~

# Nimbusware planning docs (local only — two-file model: normative plan + epics ledger)
nimbusware-orchestrator-local-plan.md
PLAN_GAP.md
plan_gap.md
releasev1features.md
e2e-testing-extension-plan.md
e2e-true-variable-launch-testing.md
benchmarks/*
